High clearance warehouse of 1,545 sqm with a detached well presented office area of 275sqm. Access is via Ryans and Martins Roads making it potentially suitable for transport operators. The large predominantly concreted site is fully fenced and options for further existing hardstand and warehousing may be available if required.
Modern and adaptable this property features everything a business needs and is offered on flexible terms.
